{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handleOpenURL:","title":"handleOpenURL:","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL","text":"NSURL"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"url"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The URL to process."}]}],"name":"url"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"YES if the URL was handled by Pushwoosh, NO otherwise.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles special Pushwoosh URLs, primarily used for:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Test device registration","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Register device for push testing via QR code"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Deep link tracking"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Process tracked deep links from push notifications","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Should be called from your app’s URL handling methods. Returns YES if the URL","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"was a Pushwoosh URL and was handled, NO if it should be processed by your app.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Example","level":2,"anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle URLs in SceneDelegate (iOS 13+):"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class SceneDelegate: UIResponder, UIWindowSceneDelegate {","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, openURLContexts URLContexts: Set<UIOpenURLContext>) {","        guard let url = URLContexts.first?.url else { return }","","        \/\/ First, check if Pushwoosh handles this URL","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            Logger.info(\"URL handled by Pushwoosh\")","            return","        }","","        \/\/ Handle other deep links","        DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, continue userActivity: NSUserActivity) {","        guard userActivity.activityType == NSUserActivityTypeBrowsingWeb,","              let url = userActivity.webpageURL else { return }","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return","        }","","        UniversalLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}","","\/\/ Legacy AppDelegate support","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ app: UIApplication,","                    open url: URL,","                    options: [UIApplication.OpenURLOptionsKey: Any] = [:]) -> Bool {","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return true","        }","","        return DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}"]}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality."}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"PWConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"abstract":[],"role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handleOpenURL:":{"role":"symbol","title":"handleOpenURL:","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"}}}